title: Ailunce Very Useful Professional Flat Top Synthetic Kabuki Brush Single Cosmetic Makeup Brush Black
description: Brushes set contains:1.Eyeliner Brush2.Lip Brush3.Eyebrow Brush4.Diagonal Brow Brush5.Eye Smudge BrushHow to clean makeup brushes:1. Run the bristles of brush under warm running water.2. Apply a small amount of gentle shampoo to bristles and work into a light lather.3. Rinse bristles thoroughly under running water. You will notice that the water leaving the brush is tinted from old makeup.4. Continue rinsing until no color leaves the brush.5. Allow it to air-dry.
